cs.RO, cs.HC, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.SY 

This paper involves the use of computational models and robotics to analyze and model non-verbal cues in human-human and human-robot interaction. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also involves human-computer interaction (cs.HC), computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), and systems and control (cs.SY) in the development and implementation of the computational models.
